"SmartSource:Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md": {"path":"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md","class_name":"SmartSource","history":[{"blocks":{"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#1/. There’s a difference between working on your note taking system, and using your note taking system to do real work. Always know which you’re doing.":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#2/. Obsidian is super powerful when you start thinking in systems":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#2/. Obsidian is super powerful when you start thinking in systems{1}":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#2/. Obsidian is super powerful when you start thinking in systems{3}":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#2/. Obsidian is super powerful when you start thinking in systems{4}":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#3/. Build systems based on how you’re working. Don’t create a system first and then try to change your behavior to fit the system":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#4/. Taking notes is easy, actually _using_ those notes is hard.{1}":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#4/. Taking notes is easy, actually _using_ those notes is hard.{2}":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#5/. Productivity ebbs and flows—build systems that support this{1}":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#5/. Productivity ebbs and flows—build systems that support this{2}":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#5/. Productivity ebbs and flows—build systems that support this{3}":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#5/. Productivity ebbs and flows—build systems that support this{4}":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#6/. Your notes are a living knowledge base, not an archive.":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#7/. New ideas come from the intersection of existing ideas":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#8/. Writing is thinking":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#9/. Publish, even if no one is watching":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#10/. Mimicry is a shortcut to success":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#10/. Mimicry is a shortcut to success#Want more Obsidian content?":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#10/. Mimicry is a shortcut to success#Want more Obsidian content?{1}":true,"Obsidian/Obsidian - 10 tips for smart usage.md#10/. Mimicry is a shortcut to success#Want more Obsidian content?{2}":true},"mtime":1726935898270,"size":10112,"hash":"ade2f30f91acd492ae960a2ad2937a38c7e608042bffced111aac9860174b739"}],"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05256739,-0.00566647,0.00992307,-0.05422316,-0.03752255,-0.03315657,0.05032247,0.06503028,-0.02936459,0.0175772,0.02417072,0.00041784,0.00617317,0.00661551,0.04026114,-0.01355285,-0.02108775,0.00627795,-0.0084497,0.01598149,0.07157461,-0.02913013,0.04642792,0.02504012,0.0328999,-0.00426895,-0.02124799,-0.03474888,-0.04799444,-0.231738,0.01507835,0.00680413,-0.00386872,0.02985599,-0.08798315,-0.03006278,-0.01412874,0.00767239,-0.07284983,0.07303166,0.0191718,0.00041145,-0.01242933,-0.02029007,-0.04961519,-0.03064747,-0.03995569,-0.01658316,0.07832968,-0.01058758,0.01770258,-0.05269734,0.01162516,-0.00429741,0.04278402,-0.03255419,0.0918439,0.02462403,0.05819689,0.01218909,0.0627576,-0.00082658,-0.1766462,0.1601695,0.00757335,0.00844207,0.00505596,0.03327433,-0.04123833,0.00229809,-0.01091659,0.08627876,-0.01188576,0.02514728,-0.00164268,-0.01199866,0.03604782,-0.03642578,-0.01569786,-0.0620301,-0.00585695,0.02550319,0.01822444,0.00125285,0.02968264,0.00649825,-0.06753725,0.05177963,0.0733482,-0.0370108,-0.03338139,-0.00965874,0.05145473,0.01925073,0.00649911,-0.0072063,0.06792713,0.01390946,-0.09682019,0.13517222,-0.03051641,-0.00302888,